{
  "info": {
    "name": "Stage 12 - 前后端集成测试 (85 cases)",
    "description": "# Knowledge Platform — Stage 12 全链路集成测试\n\n## 覆盖范围\n| 模块 | 用例数 |\n|------|--------|\n| 0-环境检查 | 4 |\n| 1-用户认证 | 9 |\n| 2-文章浏览 | 8 |\n| 3-文章创作 | 9 |\n| 4-互动模块 | 10 |\n| 5-热搜榜单 | 6 |\n| 6-AI续写 | 7 |\n| 7-我的文章 | 5 |\n| 8-数据一致性 | 5 |\n| **总计** | **63 (API)** |\n\n## 环境变量\n| 变量 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `baseUrl` | http://localhost |\n| `tokenA` | Alice 的 JWT |\n| `tokenB` | Bob 的 JWT |\n| `articleId` | 测试文章 ID |\n| `draftId` | 草稿 ID |\n\n## 执行方式\n1. Import → Create Environment (`baseUrl=http://localhost`)\n2. Run `0-环境检查` 确认服务就绪\n3. Run `1-用户认证` 按顺序执行 → token 自动保存\n4. Run `2-8` 任意顺序执行\n5. 或 Runner → Run Collection → 全量执行",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "kb-stage12"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0-环境检查 (4 cases)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "E01: 后端 trending 可达",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('HTTP 200', function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('code=200', function(){pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(200)});","console.log('✅ 后端 API 就绪');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/trending","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","trending"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "E02: 文章列表(公开GET)",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 200',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('含 PageResult 元数据',function(){pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('total');pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('list');pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('page');});","console.log('total='+j.data.total+' page='+j.data.page);"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=3","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"],"query":[{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"size","value":"3"}]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "E03: React 前端可达",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 200',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","var b=pm.response.text();","pm.test('含知识库标题',function(){pm.expect(b).to.include('知识库');});","console.log('✅ React SPA 就绪');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/","host":["{{baseUrl}}"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "E04: SPA fallback",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 200',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","pm.test('返回 index.html',function(){pm.expect(pm.response.text()).to.include('知识库');});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/#/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"]},"description":"验证 SPA fallback — 任意路由返回 index.html"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1-用户认证 (9 cases)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "A01: 注册新用户",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","if(pm.response.code===200){console.log('注册成功: '+j.data.username);pm.environment.set('testUsername','st12_'+Date.now());}","pm.test('注册成功或已存在',function(){pm.expect([200,400]).to.include(pm.response.code);});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"{{testUsername}}\",\"password\":\"test123456\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A02: 重复注册→400",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 400',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(400)});","pm.test('已存在提示',function(){pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('已存在');});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"{{testUsername}}\",\"password\":\"test123456\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A03: 空用户名→400",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 400',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(400)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"\",\"password\":\"test123456\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A04: 短密码→400",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 400',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(400)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"u1\",\"password\":\"123\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A05: Alice 登录",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","if(pm.response.code===200&&j.data.token){pm.environment.set('tokenA',j.data.token);console.log('Alice token saved');}","pm.test('登录成功',function(){pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('token');pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('tokenType','Bearer');pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('userId');});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"alice\",\"password\":\"alice123456\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","login"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A06: Bob 登录",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","if(pm.response.code===200&&j.data.token){pm.environment.set('tokenB',j.data.token);console.log('Bob token saved');}","pm.test('登录成功',function(){pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('token');});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"bob\",\"password\":\"bob123456\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","login"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A07: 错误密码→401",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 401',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(401)});","pm.test('错误提示',function(){pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('错误');});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"username\":\"alice\",\"password\":\"wrongpass\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","login"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A08: 注销",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('注销成功',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","console.log('Token 已加入黑名单');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenB}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/user/logout","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","user","logout"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A09: 注销后 Token 失效→401",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 401',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(401)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenB}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/mine","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","mine"]},"description":"使用 A08 注销的 Token 访问 → 应返回 401"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2-文章浏览 (8 cases)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "B01: 文章列表(公开,无Token)",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('HTTP 200',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","pm.test('total>0',function(){pm.expect(j.data.total).to.be.above(0)});","pm.test('page=1',function(){pm.expect(j.data.page).to.eql(1)});","pm.test('list是数组',function(){pm.expect(j.data.list).to.be.an('array')});","if(j.data.list.length>0){pm.environment.set('articleId',j.data.list[0].id);}","console.log('total='+j.data.total+' returned='+j.data.list.length);"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=5","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"],"query":[{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"size","value":"5"}]},"description":"公开 GET，无 Authorization 头"}
        },
        {
          "name": "B02: 分页第2页",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('page=2',function(){pm.expect(j.data.page).to.eql(2)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=2&size=5","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"],"query":[{"key":"page","value":"2"},{"key":"size","value":"5"}]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "B03: 文章详情(公开,无Token)",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('HTTP 200',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","pm.test('含content',function(){pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('content')});","pm.test('含likeCount',function(){pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('likeCount')});","console.log('文章: '+j.data.title);"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{articleId}}"]},"description":"公开 GET，触发阅读热度 +1"}
        },
        {
          "name": "B04: 不存在的文章→404",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('4xx错误',function(){pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([400,404]);});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/99999","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","99999"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "B05: 列表降序验证",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var list=pm.response.json().data.list;","if(list.length>=2){var ok=true;for(var i=1;i<list.length;i++){if(new Date(list[i].createdAt)>new Date(list[i-1].createdAt))ok=false;}","pm.test('按createdAt降序',function(){pm.expect(ok).to.be.true});}"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=10","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"],"query":[{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"size","value":"10"}]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "B06: 分页total正确",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('total>0(分页插件生效)',function(){pm.expect(j.data.total).to.be.above(0)});","pm.test('list长度≤size',function(){pm.expect(j.data.list.length).to.be.at.most(j.data.size)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=3","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"],"query":[{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"size","value":"3"}]},"description":"验证 total > 0（MyBatis-Plus 分页插件生效）"}
        },
        {
          "name": "B07-1: 删除文章 (准备工作)",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["if(pm.response.code===200){pm.environment.set('delArticleId',pm.response.json().data.id);console.log('待删除文章: '+pm.response.json().data.id);}"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"待删除测试\",\"content\":\"这将被删除。\",\"status\":\"PUBLISHED\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "B07-2: 删除并验证不出现在列表",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('删除成功',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","var j=JSON.parse(pm.response.text());","if(j.code===200) console.log('文章已删除，刷新列表验证其不在结果中');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"DELETE","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{delArticleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{delArticleId}}"]}}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3-文章创作 (9 cases)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "C01: 创建草稿",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('status=DRAFT',function(){pm.expect(j.data.status).to.eql('DRAFT')});","if(j.code===200){pm.environment.set('draftId',j.data.id);console.log('草稿ID: '+j.data.id);}"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"Stage12测试草稿\",\"content\":\"这是一篇测试草稿的内容。\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C02: 发布草稿",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('status=PUBLISHED',function(){pm.expect(j.data.status).to.eql('PUBLISHED')});","console.log('草稿已发布');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"PUT","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{draftId}}/publish","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{draftId}}","publish"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C03: 直接创建已发布",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('status=PUBLISHED',function(){pm.expect(j.data.status).to.eql('PUBLISHED')});","if(j.code===200)pm.environment.set('pubArticleId',j.data.id);"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"Stage12直接发布\",\"content\":\"这是直接以PUBLISHED状态创建的文章。\",\"status\":\"PUBLISHED\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C04: 修改文章",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('title已更新',function(){pm.expect(j.data.title).to.include('已修改')});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"PUT","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"(已修改) Stage12直接发布\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{pubArticleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{pubArticleId}}"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C05: 越权修改→403",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 403',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(403)});","pm.test('无权操作',function(){pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('无权');});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"PUT","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenB}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"Bob越权修改\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{pubArticleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{pubArticleId}}"]},"description":"Bob 不是作者，无权修改 Alice 的文章"}
        },
        {
          "name": "C06: 无Token创建→401",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 401',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(401)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"未认证创建\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C07: 缺少参数→400",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 400',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(400)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"title\":\"\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C08: 逻辑删除",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 200',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","console.log('文章已逻辑删除');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"DELETE","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{pubArticleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{pubArticleId}}"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "C09: 越权删除→403",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('HTTP 403',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(403)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"DELETE","header":[{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenB}}"}],"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","articles","{{articleId}}"]},"description":"Bob 删除 Alice 的文章 → 403"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4-互动模块 (10 cases)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "D01: Bob评论Alice文章",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('评论成功',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});","console.log('评论 heat+1');"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenB}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"articleId\":{{articleId}},\"content\":\"非常棒的分享！Stage12集成测试评论。\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/comments","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","comments"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "D02: 查看评论列表(公开)",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('评论列表',function(){pm.expect(j.data).to.be.an('array')});","pm.test('至少1条评论',function(){pm.expect(j.data.length).to.be.at.least(1)});","console.log('评论数: '+j.data.length);"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/comments?articleId={{articleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","comments"],"query":[{"key":"articleId","value":"{{articleId}}"}]},"description":"公开 GET，无需 Token"}
        },
        {
          "name": "D03: Alice也评论",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["pm.test('评论成功',function(){pm.response.to.have.status(200)});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"POST","header":[{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{tokenA}}"}],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"{\"articleId\":{{articleId}},\"content\":\"感谢支持！这是作者回复。\"}"},"url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/comments","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","comments"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "D04: 验证评论列表含2条",
          "event": [{"listen":"test","script":{"exec":["var j=pm.response.json();","pm.test('至少2条',function(){pm.expect(j.data.length).to.be.at.least(2)});","pm.test('按时间升序',function(){for(var i=1;i<j.data.length;i++){if(new Date(j.data[i].createdAt)<new Date(j.data[i-1].createdAt)){pm.expect.fail('顺序错误');}};pm.expect(true).to.be.true});"],"type":"text/javascript"}}],
          "request":{"method":"GET","url":{"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/api/comments?articleId={{articleId}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["api","comments"],"query":[{"key":"articleId","value":"{{articleId}}"}]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "D05: 空评论→400",
